{"tid":2490164,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《複製人徐福》討論區","createTime":"2021-04-15T11:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T04:44:50.000Z","uid":124450,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1aeb867d59054b8d763e02e87dbf41b37d2dd1e1","tid":2490164,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然覺得結局太急收尾<br />\n<br />\n入場以為係韓國動作片<br />\n睇到一半男人老狗襟唔到啲淚水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a6b5422ac04dc9243b01ce2cd4c9b743dae7b0","tid":2490164,"uid":252784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:38:36.000Z","msg":"秦始皇有冇出場"},{"pid":"ac90e1d8796b44810f545290d324951aa2b1d212","tid":2490164,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"04a6b5422ac04dc9243b01ce2cd4c9b743dae7b0","tid":2490164,"uid":252784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:38:36.000Z","msg":"秦始皇有冇出場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:41:19.000Z","msg":"套戲都有話徐福個名係來自秦始皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n編導真係真有料"},{"pid":"431cd32a270c72d9e3f8c6f3ab882ec8589f534e","tid":2490164,"uid":363347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:42:12.000Z","msg":"靜係睇咗預告<br />\n套嘢係咪講班人夾埋去喚起佢嘅感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91536fd8b9d44644de68bf37f09f370550ab284","tid":2490164,"uid":248670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:43:12.000Z","msg":"為左睇孔劉<br />\n希望多d鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b575840ee6dde2844ef21c5a6fafbe6fb337784f","tid":2490164,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:45:38.000Z","msg":"我發條慘保證套戲係值回票價<br />\n<br />\n睇感情有感情<br />\n睇哲學有哲學<br />\n睇動作有動作<br />\n睇兩個男主 兩個都發揮十足<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9f8ea666885ea77f9512ebbd1b8fb2b7d80819","tid":2490164,"uid":232229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T08:37:47.000Z","msg":"琴晚睇左<br />\n動作場面比想像中少<br />\n中間文戲長左d<br />\n最尾幾感動<br />\n寶劍做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb5d670ac717cd35c1c5aa754d66f8551bf01bc","tid":2490164,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c9f8ea666885ea77f9512ebbd1b8fb2b7d80819","tid":2490164,"uid":232229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T08:37:47.000Z","msg":"琴晚睇左<br />\n動作場面比想像中少<br />\n中間文戲長左d<br />\n最尾幾感動<br />\n寶劍做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T11:57:06.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得前段中段超水準<br />\n尾段落時間落動作場面反而曬咗個題材<br />\n<br />\n就好似本身份dse卷再考好啲就可以入醫科<br />\n宜家32分都係高 但只可以讀獸醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8a93e2f90f4657e3b7becbfa3f2183d22de231","tid":2490164,"uid":928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"樓豬，你試下入場睇第二次<br />\n呢套戲好神奇<br />\n大部分朋友都話睇第二次更好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且個ending 變得冇咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc7b84b6096b2f455e524c6818a323dd56241945","tid":2490164,"uid":5033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:58:59.000Z","msg":"屌個ending<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a165caf87e609b02eb0cc9c915ac43f54a98974","tid":24901